1635  [return: NotNull]
1636  internal static int Utf8Size([NotNull] string str) => str.Validate().Length * 4 + 1;
1637 
1645  [return: NotNull]
1646  internal static byte[] Utf8Encode([NotNull]string str, [NotNull] byte[] buffer, [NotNull] int bufferSize)
1647  {
1648  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str.Validate(), 0, str.Validate().Length, buffer, 0);
1649  buffer[str.Length] = 0;
1650  return buffer;
1651  }
1652 
1658  internal static byte[] Utf8EncodeHeap(string str)
1659  {
1660  if (str == null)
1661  {
1662  return null;
1663  }
1664 
1665  int bufferSize = Encoding.UTF8.GetByteCount(str) + 1;
1666  byte[] buffer = new byte[bufferSize];
1667  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str, 0, str.Length, buffer, 0);
1668  buffer[bufferSize - 1] = 0; // Null-terminate the string
1669 
1670  return buffer;
1671  }
1672 
1673 
1680  public static string Utf8ToManaged(IntPtr s, bool freePtr = false)
1681  {
1682  if (s == IntPtr.Zero)
1683  {
1684  return null;
1685  }
1686 
1687  int len = 0;
1688  while (Marshal.ReadByte(s, len) != 0)
1689  {
1690  len++;
1691  }
1692 
1693  if (len == 0)
1694  {
1695  return string.Empty;
1696  }
1697 
1698  byte[] bytes = new byte[len];
1699  Marshal.Copy(s, bytes, 0, len);
1700  string result = Encoding.UTF8.GetString(bytes);
1701 
1702  if (freePtr)
1703  {
1704  SDL_free(s);
1705  }
1706 
1707  return result;
1708  }

1719  private static uint SDL_FOURCC(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => (uint) (a | (b << 8) | (c << 16) | (d << 24));

2632  public static void SDL_LogGetOutputFunction(

2634  out IntPtr userdata
2635  )

2637  SDL_LogGetOutputFunction(
2638  out IntPtr result,
2639  out userdata
2640  );
2641  if (result != IntPtr.Zero)
2642  {
2643  callback = (SdlLogOutputFunction) Marshal.GetDelegateForFunctionPointer(
2644  result,
2645  typeof(SdlLogOutputFunction)
2646  );
2647  }
2648  else

2650  callback = null;

2672  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_ShowMessageBox", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
2673  private static extern int INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox([In] ref InternalSdlMessageBoxData messageboxdata, out int buttonid);
2674 
2675 
2681  private static IntPtr INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(string str)
2682  {
2683  if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(str))
2684  {
2685  return IntPtr.Zero;
2686  }
2687 
2688  byte[] bytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0');
2689  IntPtr mem = SDL_malloc(bytes.Length);
2690  Marshal.Copy(bytes, 0, mem, bytes.Length);
2691  return mem;
2692  }
2693 
2700  public static int SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref SdlMessageBoxData messageboxdata, out int buttonid)
2701  {
2702  InternalSdlMessageBoxData data = new InternalSdlMessageBoxData
2703  {
2704  flags = messageboxdata.flags,
2705  window = messageboxdata.window,
2706  title = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.title),
2707  message = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.message),
2708  numbuttons = messageboxdata.numbuttons
2709  };
2710 
2711  InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[] buttons = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[messageboxdata.numbuttons];
2712  IntPtr buttonsPtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2713 
2714  try
2715  {
2716  for (int i = 0; i < messageboxdata.numbuttons; i++)
2717  {
2718  buttons[i] = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData
2719  {
2720  flags = messageboxdata.buttons[i].flags,
2721  buttonId = messageboxdata.buttons[i].buttonId,
2722  text = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.buttons[i].text)
2723  };
2724  }
2725 
2726  buttonsPtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(buttons.Length * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>());
2727  for (int i = 0; i < buttons.Length; i++)
2728  {
2729  IntPtr buttonPtr = buttonsPtr + i * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>();
2730  Marshal.StructureToPtr(buttons[i], buttonPtr, false);
2731  }
2732 
2733  data.buttons = buttonsPtr;
2734 
2735  IntPtr colorSchemePtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2736  if (messageboxdata.colorScheme != null)
2737  {
2738  colorSchemePtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(Marshal.SizeOf<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>());
2739  Marshal.StructureToPtr(messageboxdata.colorScheme.Value, colorSchemePtr, false);
2740  }
2741 
2742  int result = INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref data, out buttonid);
2743 
2744  for (int i = 0; i < messageboxdata.numbuttons; i++)
2745  {
2746  SDL_free(buttons[i].text);
2747  }
2748 
2749  SDL_free(data.message);
2750  SDL_free(data.title);
2751 
2752  if (colorSchemePtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2753  {
2754  Marshal.DestroyStructure<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>(colorSchemePtr);
2755  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(colorSchemePtr);
2756  }
2757 
2758  return result;
2759  }
2760  finally
2761  {
2762  if (buttonsPtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2763  {
2764  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(buttonsPtr);
2765  }
2766  }
2767  }
2768

5974 
5983  private static uint SDL_DEFINE_PIXELFOURCC(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => SDL_FOURCC(a, b, c, d);
5984 
5994  private static uint SDL_DEFINE_PIXELFORMAT(
5995  SdlPixelType type,
5996  uint order,
5997  SdlPackedLayout layout,
5998  byte bits,
5999  byte bytes
6000  )
6001  => (uint) (
6002  (1 << 28) |
6003  ((byte) type << 24) |
6004  ((byte) order << 20) |
6005  ((byte) layout << 16) |
6006  (bits << 8) |
6007  bytes
6008  );
6009 
6015  private static byte SDL_PIXELFLAG(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 28) & 0x0F);
6016 
6022  private static byte SDL_PIXELTYPE(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 24) & 0x0F);
6023 
6029  private static byte SDL_PIXELORDER(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 20) & 0x0F);
6030 
6036  public static byte SDL_PIXELLAYOUT(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 16) & 0x0F);
6037 
6043  public static byte SDL_BITSPERPIXEL(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 8) & 0xFF);
6044 
6050  public static byte SDL_BYTESPERPIXEL(uint x)
6051  {
6052  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(x))
6053  {
6054  if (x == SdlPixelFormatYuy2 ||
6055  x == SdlPixelFormatUy ||
6056  x == SdlPixelFormatYv)
6057  {
6058  return 2;
6059  }
6060 
6061  return 1;
6062  }
6063 
6064  return (byte) (x & 0xFF);
6065  }
6066 
6072  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_INDEXED(uint format)
6073  {
6074  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6075  {
6076  return false;
6077  }
6078 
6079  SdlPixelType pType =
6080  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6081  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex1 ||
6082  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex4 ||
6083  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex8;
6084  }
6085 
6091  private static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_PACKED(uint format)
6092  {
6093  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6094  {
6095  return false;
6096  }
6097 
6098  SdlPixelType pType =
6099  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6100  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked8 ||
6101  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked16 ||
6102  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked32;
6103  }
6104 
6110  private static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ARRAY(uint format)
6111  {
6112  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6113  {
6114  return false;
6115  }
6116 
6117  SdlPixelType pType =
6118  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6119  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu8 ||
6120  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu16 ||
6121  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu32 ||
6122  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf16 ||
6123  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf32;
6124  }
6125 
6131  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ALPHA(uint format)
6132  {
6133  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_PACKED(format))
6134  {
6135  SdlPackedOrder pOrder =
6136  (SdlPackedOrder) SDL_PIXELORDER(format);
6137  return pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderArgb ||
6138  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderRgba ||
6139  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderAbgr ||
6140  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderBgra;
6141  }
6142 
6143  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ARRAY(format))
6144  {
6145  SdlArrayOrder aOrder =
6146  (SdlArrayOrder) SDL_PIXELORDER(format);
6147  return aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderArgb ||
6148  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderRgba ||
6149  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderAbgr ||
6150  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderBgra;
6151  }
6152 
6153  return false;
6154  }

7399  public static SdlBool SDL_GetEventFilter(
7400  out SdlEventFilter filter,
7401  out IntPtr userdata
7402  )
7403  {
7404  SdlBool val = SDL_GetEventFilter(out IntPtr result, out userdata);
7405  if (result != IntPtr.Zero)
7406  {
7407  filter = (SdlEventFilter) Marshal.GetDelegateForFunctionPointer(
7408  result,
7409  typeof(SdlEventFilter)
7410  );
7411  }
7412  else
7413  {
7414  filter = null;
7415  }
7416 
7417  return val;
7418  }

8862  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]

8864  IntPtr gameController,
8865  SdlGameControllerAxis axis
8866  );
8867 
8874  public static SdlGameControllerButtonBind SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis(
8875  IntPtr gameController,
8876  SdlGameControllerAxis axis
8877  )
8878  {
8879  // This is guaranteed to never be null
8880  InternalSdlGameControllerButtonBind dumb = INTERNAL_SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis(
8881  gameController,
8882  axis
8883  );
8884  SdlGameControllerButtonBind result = new SdlGameControllerButtonBind
8885  {
8886  bindType = (SdlGameControllerBindType) dumb.bindType
8887  };
8888  result.value.hat.hat = dumb.unionVal0;
8889  result.value.hat.hat_mask = dumb.unionVal1;
8890  return result;
8891  }
